# Decision Capture for traceflux
# Purpose: Route traceflux decisions to Issue vs Docs
# Usage: workflow check workflow/decision-capture.workflow.list
#
# Philosophy:
#   Issue = Temporary decisions (< 6 months, traceflux-specific)
#   Docs = Permanent rules (timeless principles)

import: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tracer-mohist/workflow-as-list/refs/heads/main/examples/decision/route.workflow.list

# traceflux-specific customization:
# - Issue template: .github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/decision.yml
# - Docs target: docs/ directory
# - Labels: decision, tmp
